---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="Layanan Penerbitan — PT Penerbit Quran Indonesia">

<PageHero
  title="Layanan Penerbitan"
  subtitle="Solusi lengkap dari naskah hingga buku di tangan pembaca"
  breadcrumb="Layanan"
/>

<section class="py-[88px]">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-7">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.14em] uppercase text-gold flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 mb-4 font-sans">
        <span class="w-7 h-[1.5px] bg-gold"></span>
        Apa yang Kami Tawarkan
        <span class="w-7 h-[1.5px] bg-gold"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(24px,3vw,34px)] font-black text-surface-6 leading-[1.2] mb-3">
        Layanan <em class="not-italic text-emerald">Profesional</em> Kami
      </h2>
      <p class="text-surface-4 text-[15px] font-sans max-w-[520px] mx-auto leading-[1.8]">
        Dari naskah mentah hingga buku berkualitas tinggi siap edar — kami menangani setiap tahapan dengan standar terbaik.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-7 border border-surface-2/50 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-emerald"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">📝</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-surface-3 font-sans">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-[17px] mb-2.5">Penerbitan Buku Lengkap</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
          Layanan end-to-end dari penerimaan naskah, editing, desain, layout, cetak, hingga buku siap edar. Solusi satu pintu untuk menerbitkan karya Anda.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-7 border border-surface-2/50 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-emerald"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">✏️</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-surface-3 font-sans">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-[17px] mb-2.5">Editing Naskah</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
          Penyuntingan substantif, copy editing, dan proofreading oleh editor berpengalaman untuk memastikan naskah Anda tampil sempurna.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-7 border border-surface-2/50 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-emerald"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">🎨</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-surface-3 font-sans">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-[17px] mb-2.5">Layout & Desain</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
          Desain cover premium dan layout isi sesuai standar nasional. Tampilan profesional yang menarik perhatian pembaca.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-7 border border-surface-2/50 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-emerald"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">🖨️</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-surface-3 font-sans">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-[17px] mb-2.5">Cetak Buku</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
          Dicetak dengan mesin modern dan kertas berkualitas tinggi. Hasil tajam, warna akurat, dan tahan lama.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-7 border border-surface-2/50 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-emerald"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">🌐</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-surface-3 font-sans">05</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-[17px] mb-2.5">Distribusi Buku</h3>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
          Distribusi ke toko buku, marketplace, dan lembaga pendidikan Islam di seluruh Indonesia.
        </p>
      </div>

      <a href="/nuurkids" class="bg-nk-cream rounded-lg p-7 border border-gold/20 relative overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group block">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-gold"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
          <span class="text-3xl">📚</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-gold/50 font-sans">✦</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-nk-brown text-[17px] mb-2.5">Penerbitan NUURKIDS</h3>
        <p class="text-nk-brown/70 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8] mb-4">
          Buku anak muslim premium dengan standar internasional. Konten Islami edukatif dengan ilustrasi dan desain berkelas dunia.
        </p>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gold text-xs font-semibold font-sans group-hover:gap-2.5 transition-all duration-300">
          Selengkapnya
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald to-emerald-light relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 iso-pattern-white"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-7 py-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-white text-[clamp(24px,3vw,34px)] font-black mb-3">
      Siap Menerbitkan Buku Anda?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-white/70 text-[15px] font-sans max-w-[460px] mx-auto mb-8 leading-[1.8]">
      Konsultasikan naskah Anda dengan tim kami. Kami siap membantu dari awal hingga buku Anda sampai di tangan pembaca.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/penulis" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-[26px] py-3 rounded bg-white text-emerald text-sm font-semibold font-sans hover:bg-gold-pale hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-medium transition-all duration-300">
        Panduan Penulis
      </a>
      <a href="/kontak" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-[26px] py-3 rounded text-white text-sm font-semibold font-sans border-[1.5px] border-white/40 hover:bg-white/10 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300">
        Hubungi Kami
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
